@honeyboy478

you are not replacing any files, you're only going to move the folder DLC in the Borderlands\WillowGame\CookedPC

since originally, the DLC folder don't exist in the \Borderlands\WillowGame\CookedPC if you haven't installed or downloaded any DLC's.

@AnthonyTjuatja and anyone else asking the same question

yes you will be able to play it online, even with a cracked copy of the game you can play it online, this isn't like games such as COD4 where you have to enter a registration key to install or play it online all you do is install the game (legit or not) and patch to the latest version, the only thing that will stop you from playing online is if you dont have a cracked .exe file to run the game and you encounter the insert CD error in which case either get the cracked exe from somewhere or if you bought the game insert your disk.

the game and game spy dont check anything to determine whether or not its a legit copy of the game or whether the DLC"s you have are legit it takes them at face value and passes them as legit. Unless you installed the DLC's incorrectly you can play them online with other people regardless of store-purchased, STEAM bought or cracked.

@Xmass

Open the folder where all the files are, and right click the one at the top and click extract.

